mkfontscale
------------------------------------------
X.Org scalable font file indexer

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.25-15
  libbz2_1-1.0.5-2
  libfontenc1-1.0.4-1
  libfreetype6-2.3.8-1
  zlib-1.2.3-2

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding devel packages)
  autoconf2.5-2.63-1
  automake1.10-1.10.1-2
  binutils-20080624-2
  cygport-0.4.4-1
  gawk-3.1.6-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-3
  make-3.81-2
  pkg-config-0.23a-2
  sed-4.1.5-2
  xorg-util-macros-1.2.1-1

Canonical website:
  http://xorg.freedesktop.org/

Canonical download:
  http://xorg.freedesktop.org/releases/individual/app/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack mkfontscale-1.0.6-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  cygport ./mkfontscale-1.0.6-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/mkfontscale-1.0.6-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/mkfontscale-1.0.6-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/bin/mkfontscale.exe
  /usr/share/doc/mkfontscale-1.0.6/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/mkfontscale-1.0.6/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/man/man1/mkfontscale.1.gz

------------------

